Connection refused or timeout <p>Local Deployment: </p><pre><code># Check port forwarding
ps aux | grep "kubectl port-forward"

# Restart port forwarding if needed
export OC_PROJECT=default
kubectl port-forward -n $OC_PROJECT deployment/geofm-ui 4180:4180 &gt;&gt; studio-pf.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;
</code></pre><p></p> <p>Cluster Deployment: </p><pre><code># Check ingress/route
kubectl get ingress -n &lt;namespace&gt;
oc get routes -n &lt;namespace&gt;
</code></pre><p></p>

Cluster Deployment <pre><code># List Helm releases
helm list -n &lt;namespace&gt;

# Get Helm release status
helm status geospatial-studio -n &lt;namespace&gt;

# Get Helm values
helm get values geospatial-studio -n &lt;namespace&gt;

# Check Helm history
helm history geospatial-studio -n &lt;namespace&gt;
</code></pre>
